game.name: LTV Car Park Training School
game.description:
Different countries use different areas for car parking, but parking rules generally remain the same! Do you want to learn about multiple car parking areas while also improving your knowledge about the latest driving rules? If so, join LTV Car Park Training School and be prepared to learn about car parking and car driving skills. Choose your car, complete mission, earn money and then upgrade your vehicles using that money in this brand new racing challenge!

There are multiple levels and maps to play through. When you click the play button, you will see a car that you have to park in a designated area. You will be rewarded with some coins for your every successful car parking mission. Click the gas button in PC or tap the screen of your mobile phone to move your car forward! Do not forget to click the brake button to stop your vehicle if it reaches at the parking slot. Give it left or right direction if needed to change the direction of your vehicle in this HTML5 parking game!

Be careful as you would have three lives to use in this car driving simulator! Change the camera view by clicking the camera button shown on the left upper portion of the screen! Try to complete your mission as fast as you can to grab 3 stars rating in each level! Hurry up friends as the time is running! Upgrade your vehicles and get a chance to drive and park advanced car models with the help of coins you earn along the way! Play other popular titles from the category of free parking games in case of seeking extra fun!
